column4: hey guys can someone help me get my usb wifi dongle working??
have you read the WifiDocs yet?
read that and if you have any questions or run into problems please feel free to ask here
it doesnt have usb there just pci
provide me with some details of the make/model and I'll take a look
it shows up on the lsusb
would it be possible for you to pastebin the output from 'iwconfig' and 'dmesg | grep rt2'
all the details are on my laptop

most people would need to look at the output of those two commands that I gave too you before they would be able to help. as a wild guess I remember that there was issues with rt2800usb and rt2870sta fighting, you could try blacklisting rt2800usb by doing 'sudo gedit /etc/modprobe.d/blacklist.conf' and adding 'rt2800usb'
i can save them and import them to you
paste the URL of the pasebin to me in this channel when you have done so and I'll take a look

sorry I actually have to leave right now but if you gather a pastebin of the output of the two commands that I gave you I'm sure that someone else will be able to help - if not I'll take a look when I return
